<h2 class="site-portfolio__title--blue">Design</h2>

<p>For the design of the website our group immediately agreed to a mobile-first design and then scaling up to desktop. We each made our own wireframes, before sharing them with the rest of the group and then creating our final design based off each others ideas.</p>

<img src="/images/portfolio/love-manchester-website/love-manchester-ui.jpg" alt="Three screenshots of the Love Manchester website in desktop and mobile sizes." />

<p>When it came to structuring the website we wanted to make it as simple as possible. Using large blocks where neccessary to make them stand out and using a simple navigation so the user can naviagte round the website with ease.</p>

